sentences: Díaz was born in a farm named "La Casa de Alto Pino" in the locality known as Lagunita de la Sierra then corregimiento of Hatonuevo in the Commissary of La Guajira which in 1928 pertained to the municipality of Barrancas.
On October 4, 1948 Díaz decided to move to Hatonuevo where he participated in numerous parties with friends and which he was always asked to sing.
In 1993 Ivo composed the song "Dame tu Alma" to honor his father.

sentences: Leandro José Díaz Duarte (February 20, 1928 – June 22, 2013) was a Colombian vallenato music composer.
His parents took him to the Virgin of El Carmen festivities every year, vacation time in which his cousins visited him and sang to him for fun.
He composed his first song at the age of 17 years and named it "La Loba de Ceniza".
